file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Auth Component
  description: Component
  version: 1.0.0

paths: {}

components:
  schemas:
    MultiplePoint:
      type: object
      required:
        - total
        - points
      properties:
        total:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        points:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Point'
    SinglePoint:
      type: object
      required:
        - point
      properties:
        point:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Point'
    Point:
      type: object
      required:
        - id
        - name
        - resource_owner_id
        - location
        - altitude
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        name:
          type: string
        location:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Location'
        altitude:
          type: number
          format: float
        labels:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: './general.yml#/components/schemas/Label'
        description:
          type: string
        display_info:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: './general.yml#/components/schemas/DisplayInfo'
        resource_owner_id:
          type: string
          format: uuid
    PointRequest:
      type: object
      required:
        - resource_owner_id
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        location:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Location'
        altitude:
          type: number
          format: float
        labels:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: './general.yml#/components/schemas/Label'
        description:
          type: string
        display_info:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: './general.yml#/components/schemas/DisplayInfo'
        resource_owner_id:
          type: string
    MultipleCircle:
      type: object
      properties:
        total:
          type: integer
          format: int64

        circles:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Circle'
    SingleCircle:
      type: object
      properties:
        circle:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Circle'
    Circle:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        name:
          type: string
        altitude:
          type: number
          format: float
        radius_m:
          type: number
          format: float
        location:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Location'
        labels:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: './general.yml#/components/schemas/Label'
        description:
          type: string
        display_info:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: './general.yml#/components/schemas/DisplayInfo'
        resource_owner_id:
          type: string
    MultipleRoute:
      type: object
      properties:
        total:
          type: integer
          format: int64

        routes:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Route'
    SingleRoute:
      type: object
      properties:
        route:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Route'
    Route:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        name:
          type: string
        contents:
          type: array
          items:
            type: object
            properties:
              order_no:
                type: integer
              type:
                type: string
              id:
                type: string
        labels:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: './general.yml#/components/schemas/Label'
        description:
          type: string
        display_info:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: './general.yml#/components/schemas/DisplayInfo'
        resource_owner_id:
          type: string
    Location:
      required:
        - latitude
        - longitude
      type: object
      properties:
        latitude:
          type: number
        longitude:
          type: number
